    <h1>12 BEST BUYS AT JEWELUXE 2020 SICIS JEW&#xAD;ELS HIGH JEW&#xAD;ELLERY IRIS EAR&#xAD;RINGS ($29,800) FARAONE MENNELLA &#x2018;STELLA&#x2019; EAR&#xAD;RINGS ($3,050)</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201204/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-12-04"><time>2020-12-04</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>1</p>
    <p>EM­PIRE TREA­SURES EMER­ALD EAR­RINGS ($8,993)</p>
    <p>Emer­ald lovers will ap­pre­ci­ate the six rare, heart-shaped emer­alds (to­talling 4.13 carats) in th­ese glit­ter­ing ear­rings, which are also embellishe­d with 84 pieces of round di­a­monds (1.15 carats) and white gold.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at: Em­pire Trea­sures at Scotts Square</p>
    <p>2</p>
    <p>PAOLO COSTAGLI BRIL­LANTE EAR­RINGS ($5,438)</p>
    <p>In­spired by con­fi­dent and strong women, New York-based de­signer Paolo Costagli’s con­tem­po­rary pieces marry bold but time­less de­signs, like this pair of 18-karat rose gold Bril­lante ear­rings with white di­a­monds.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at: Lee Hwa Di­a­mond Prom­e­nade at Ion Or­chard un­til Dec 20</p>
    <p>Vi­brant amethyst and white di­a­monds come to­gether in this in­tri­cate piece of mi­cro­mo­saic jew­ellery – a tra­di­tional craft form with a painstak­ing process of cre­at­ing art from tiny frag­ments of tesserae.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at: El­liott & Car­men at Raf­fles Ho­tel</p>
    <p>Th­ese unas­sum­ing hoops with turquoise and gold links cat­a­pulted the late Italian fine jew­ellery de­signer Roberto Faraone Mennella to fame af­ter they ap­peared on the ears of sex-crazed Sa­man­tha Jones (Kim Cat­trall) in an episode of tele­vi­sion show Sex And The City.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at: El­liott & Car­men at Raf­fles Ho­tel</p>
    <p>7</p>
    <p>KHOE STARRY DI­A­MOND NECK­LACE ($618)</p>
    <p>This dainty 18-karat gold neck­lace fea­tures a sin­gle di­a­mond sus­pended on a golden star – in­spired by the North Star Po­laris, a sym­bol of hope, guid­ance and wis­dom. Avail­able at: Gold­heart Jew­elry</p>
    <p>4 LEONORI</p>
    <p>GIOIELLI VIC­TO­RIA RING (FROM $3,978)</p>
    <p>In­spired by a new baby born into the Leonori fam­ily of jewellers, the Vic­to­ria col­lec­tion rep­re­sents the pu­rity and com­plex­ity of a new­born – seen in the dainty egg with white di­a­monds (0.21 carats) in 18-karat white, rose or yel­low gold.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at: Lee Hwa Di­a­mond Prom­e­nade at Ion Or­chard un­til Dec 20</p>
    <p>MA­RINA B PNEU EAR­RINGS</p>
    <p>(PRICE UPON RE­QUEST)</p>
    <p>The “B” in Ma­rina B stands for Bul­gari – de­signer Ma­rina Bul­gari left her fam­ily’s famed maison in 1976 to launch her epony­mous la­bel of in­no­va­tive jew­ellery. This pair of ear­rings with 11.85-carat black jade comes with de­tach­able, in­ter­change­able beads in dif­fer­ent-coloured Rus­sian Quartz.</p>
    <p>Avail­able at: El­liott & Car­men at Raf­fles Ho­tel</p>

